translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あ？　ククルククルは何故そんなことをってか？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Huh? Why did Kukurukuru do something like that?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「さあな、気まぐれかなんかじゃねぇか？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Who knows? Maybe it was just a whim or something."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「結局、ククルククルが何を考えていたか……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "In the end, what Kukurukuru was thinking..."},{

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 俺には何一つ分からずじまいだったな……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I didn't understand a single thing..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「魔人になった俺様の生活はそこから、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "My life as a demon changed completely from there,"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 一変した……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: it was transformed..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「なーんてことにならなかったんだよなぁ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "But nothing like that actually happened."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 残念ながら」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Unfortunately."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「魔王の血を飲んだってのに俺様は弱いまま……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Even though I drank the Demon King's blood, I remained weak..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ちょっと体力や力は上がったが
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I gained a bit of stamina and strength,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 俺より強い奴なんてごまんといた」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: but there were countless others stronger than me."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「だから……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "That's why..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「だから、必死に必死に必死に生き延びたぜ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "That's why I desperately, desperately struggled to survive..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 俺には夢があったからな……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Because I had a dream..."
"A dream?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「それはなに？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "What was it?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ケイブリス様、いつもそこだけボカす……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Lord Kebris, you always blur out just that part..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「それはなぁ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Well..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「それは……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "It is..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 弱く、小さく、ふとしたことで死ぬ、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Weak, small, dying from trivial causes,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 脆弱なリスが見た夢。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A fragile squirrel's dream.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それは……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That is...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「くくく……いつか教えてやるよ……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Heh heh heh... I'll tell you someday..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「とにかく、その頃から決意したんだ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Anyway, from that time on, I made a determination."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「いつか、絶対に強くなる、ってな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "That someday, I will definitely become strong."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ズンズンとベズドグ山の中を進む
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They steadily advance into Mount Bezdog.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスの前にフレイアが横から現れる。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Freya appears from the side in front of Rance.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「総統、止まりなさい」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Commander, stop."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 無言で廊下の角を指し示す。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: She silently points to the corner of the corridor.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: （む……声がするな……）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: (Hmm... I hear a voice...)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「くそ、ケイブリスの奴！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Damn it, that Kebris guy!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 俺らをこんな場所に飼い殺しにしやがって……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: He keeps us caged up in a place like this..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ははは、まーたその話かよ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Hahaha, that story again?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「左遷か、栄転か……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Demotion or promotion...?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: こんな場所じゃすること何もないんだよな……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: There's nothing to do in a place like this..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「いいんじゃねーの？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Isn't it fine?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: とりあえず安全地帯なのは間違いねーんだし」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: At least it's definitely a safe zone."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「体が鈍っちまうよ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "My body is getting sluggish!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: はー、敵、敵、敵、攻めてこねーかな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Haah, enemies, enemies, enemies, I hope they attack."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ははは、いるわけねーだろ、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Hahaha, there's no way anyone would,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: こんな魔物界の奥地にある、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: come to such a remote part of the monster realm,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: こんな危険な山に来る奴なんてよ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: or to a dangerous mountain like this."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「がははは、それはどうかな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Gahahaha, I wonder about that."
"Huh?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ぎゃああああああああ！？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Gyaaaaaaaah!?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「俺様参上！　がははははは！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I have arrived! Gahahahaha!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスの登場に魔物兵の一人は溜め息を吐いた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: At Rance's appearance, one of the monster soldiers sighed.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「おいおい、まさか本当に
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Hey, hey, I can't believe someone would actually

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: こんな場所に攻めてくる奴がいるとは……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: come to attack a place like this..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ちっ、仕方ねぇな……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Tch, it can't be helped..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「総員、戦闘用意！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Everyone, prepare for battle!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 勝てば、上玉女の褒美つきだぞ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If we win, there will be rewards with high-quality women!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「うひょー！　死ね死ね死ねー！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Woohoo! Die, die, die!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「む、門番って奴か……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Hmm, so this is a gate guard..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 巨大な扉の前には、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: In front of the huge door,
